<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink46-kilavi">
      <p type="edition">maṉaikkaṇ varutal parattai vilakka vilaṅkip piṉpu ulakiyalpaṟṟi avaḷ kuṟippiṉōṭum vantamai aṟinta tōḻi talaimakaṉaip pulantu colliyatu.</p>
      <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="Aink46">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>niṉakkē yaṉṟaḵ temakkumā riṉitē</l>
<l>niṉmārpu nayanta naṉṉuta larivai</l>
<l>vēṇṭiya kuṟippiṉai yāki</l>
<l>yīṇṭunī yaruḷā tāṇṭuṟai tallē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">


<l>   It is [sweet] not only for you, [but] for us too it is sweet</l> 
<l>   – [your] staying there, [since] you cannot be considerate here, </l> 
<l>   since you've got it into your head to lust after</l> 
<l>   the young woman with a fine forehead who yearns for your chest.</l> 
  
            
  
  
          </lg>
    </div>
